Faith-Forming Experiences for the Church, by the Church.

Youth Unlimited provides week-long mission experiences and other faith-forming events for middle and high school age students. We passionately strive to help youth leaders challenge youth to commit their lives to Jesus Christ and transform this world for him.
• SERVE Youth Mission Trips:Students on SERVE mission trips participate in revitalizing communities, showing compassion for the marginalized, providing recreation for children, performing acts of kindness and sharing the Gospel.
• LIVE IT Youth Conference:LIVE IT is a week-long event where students learn about their value in Christ, while learning how to use the talents God has given them to spread his love to their friends, community and world around them.

The Youth Unlimited Mission 

“Youth Unlimited helps churches challenge youth to commit their lives to Jesus Christ and transform this world for him.”

Youth Unlimited is a non-denominational, non-profit ministry organization with the focus of assisting the Church and its many local congregations with their ministry to our youth. We strongly believe that the local church is the tool God longs to use to reveal himself to this world. We know that taking the call of ministering to youth today is not easy or for the faint of heart. Therefore, we are blessed by encouraging, supporting, equipping and partnering with congregations across North America to reach this generation for Jesus Christ!

Core Values

We value being centered on Christ, the transformation of lives, operating within the context of the church, missional living, proclaiming the gospel to youth in a way that is relevant to them, a reformed perspective, building and valuing personal relationships and relationships with God, and intentional inclusiveness and diversity (ethically, culturally and denominationally).


Ministry Partners

Youth Unlimited is one of three ministries incorporated in an organization called Dynamic Youth Ministries. GEMS Girls’ Club is a ministry for young girls and Cadets is the companion ministry for boys. Youth Unlimited is the co-ed ministry for high school youth.
